{"name":"【英文】AI搜索引擎卡片模版","dsl":{"schema":"2.0","config":{"update_multi":true,"style":{"text_size":{"normal_v2":{"default":"normal","pc":"normal","mobile":"heading"}},"color":{"color_wp8cibqdfnf":{"light_mode":"rgba(252, 249, 226, 1)","dark_mode":"rgba(37, 35, 15, 1)"},"color_ru9m8pepwo":{"light_mode":"rgba(252, 249, 226, 1)","dark_mode":"rgba(37, 35, 15, 1)"},"color_le4fkwmd6q":{"light_mode":"rgba(252, 249, 226, 1)","dark_mode":"rgba(37, 35, 15, 1)"},"color_7h9pis8f4qp":{"light_mode":"rgba(252, 249, 226, 1)","dark_mode":"rgba(37, 35, 15, 1)"},"color_e5ki3ewtg0e":{"light_mode":"rgba(252, 249, 226, 1)","dark_mode":"rgba(37, 35, 15, 1)"},"color_7y9dfemkq3":{"light_mode":"rgba(252, 249, 226, 1)","dark_mode":"rgba(37, 35, 15, 1)"}}}},"body":{"direction":"vertical","elements":[{"tag":"img","img_key":"img_v3_02121_3388f9ee-f666-4ca6-9614-98dbd0b3af5g","preview":true,"transparent":false,"scale_type":"fit_horizontal","alt":{"tag":"plain_text","content":""}},{"tag":"markdown","content":"**Key Capabilities**","text_align":"left","text_size":"heading","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px","icon":{"tag":"standard_icon","token":"score_outlined","color":"red"},"element_id":"title_key"},{"tag":"column_set","horizontal_spacing":"8px","horizontal_align":"left","columns":[{"tag":"column","width":"weighted","background_style":"red-50","elements":[{"tag":"markdown","content":"**<font color='red'>🔥 应用新增支持 “物品池” 配置能力</font>**","text_align":"left","text_size":"normal_v2","element_id":"key_1_title"},{"tag":"markdown","content":"**配置前置过滤条件**：支持通过前置过滤条件圈定应用内可参与搜索、问答与推荐的有效物品范围，企业可基于业务规则筛选生效数据，仅处理符合条件的物品，减少无效数据带来的处理与计算成本。\n**自动更新物品池**：当物品字段发生变更，或物品进入 / 超出设定时间范围时，平台可自动更新物品池，并同步完成搜索索引、Embedding 及推荐倒排结果的新增、过滤与清理，确保可搜索、可推荐的有效物品范围始终与配置条件保持一致。","text_align":"left","text_size":"normal_v2","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px","element_id":"key_1_body"},{"tag":"img","img_key":"img_v2_9dd98485-2900-4d65-ada9-e31d1408dcfg","preview":true,"transparent":false,"scale_type":"fit_horizontal","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px","element_id":"key_1_picture"}],"padding":"12px 12px 12px 12px","direction":"vertical","horizontal_spacing":"8px","vertical_spacing":"8px","horizontal_align":"left","vertical_align":"top","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px","element_id":"section_key_1","weight":1}],"margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px"},{"tag":"markdown","content":"**General Capabilities**","text_align":"left","text_size":"heading","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px","icon":{"tag":"standard_icon","token":"setting-inter_outlined","color":"blue"},"element_id":"title_common"},{"tag":"column_set","flex_mode":"stretch","horizontal_spacing":"12px","horizontal_align":"left","columns":[{"tag":"column","width":"weighted","background_style":"color_7h9pis8f4qp","elements":[{"tag":"markdown","content":"**<font color='orange'> 📑 应用新增支持 “物品池” 配置能力</font>**","text_align":"left","text_size":"normal_v2","element_id":"common_1_title"},{"tag":"markdown","content":"**配置前置过滤条件**：支持通过前置过滤条件圈定应用内可参与搜索、问答与推荐的有效物品范围，企业可基于业务规则筛选生效数据，仅处理符合条件的物品，减少无效数据带来的处理与计算成本。\n**自动更新物品池**：当物品字段发生变更，或物品进入 / 超出设定时间范围时，平台可自动更新物品池，并同步完成搜索索引、Embedding 及推荐倒排结果的新增、过滤与清理，确保可搜索、可推荐的有效物品范围始终与配置条件保持一致。","text_align":"left","text_size":"normal_v2","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px","element_id":"common_1_body"},{"tag":"img","img_key":"img_v2_9dd98485-2900-4d65-ada9-e31d1408dcfg","preview":true,"transparent":false,"scale_type":"fit_horizontal","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px","element_id":"common_1_picture"}],"padding":"12px 12px 12px 12px","direction":"vertical","horizontal_spacing":"8px","vertical_spacing":"4px","horizontal_align":"left","vertical_align":"top","element_id":"section_common_1","weight":1}],"margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px"},{"tag":"column_set","horizontal_spacing":"8px","horizontal_align":"left","columns":[{"tag":"column","width":"weighted","background_style":"color_e5ki3ewtg0e","elements":[{"tag":"markdown","content":"**<font color='orange'>📋 控制台新增支持 “复制数据集配置” 能力</font>**","text_align":"left","text_size":"normal_v2","element_id":"common_2_title"},{"tag":"markdown","content":"**一键复制已有数据集配置**：可在控制台直接复制当前数据集的基础配置，快速生成新的数据集，减少重复创建、重复配置带来的接入成本。复制后的数据集可进一步修改数据集名称、描述、绑定应用、字段类型、字段属性及索引配置，更方便适配不同业务场景下的数据要求。\n**按需选择复制范围**：支持选择仅复制数据集配置，快速复用原有 schema、字段类型、索引及展示样式等；也支持选择同时复制数据集配置与数据，满足从模板复用到整体迁移的不同场景需求。","text_align":"left","text_size":"normal_v2","element_id":"common_2_body"},{"tag":"img","img_key":"img_v2_9dd98485-2900-4d65-ada9-e31d1408dcfg","preview":true,"transparent":false,"scale_type":"fit_horizontal","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px","element_id":"common_2_picture"}],"padding":"12px 12px 12px 12px","direction":"vertical","horizontal_spacing":"8px","vertical_spacing":"4px","horizontal_align":"left","vertical_align":"top","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px","element_id":"section_common_2","weight":1}],"margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px"},{"tag":"column_set","horizontal_spacing":"8px","horizontal_align":"left","columns":[{"tag":"column","width":"weighted","background_style":"color_7y9dfemkq3","elements":[{"tag":"markdown","content":"**<font color='orange'>📋 控制台新增支持 “复制数据集配置” 能力</font>**","text_align":"left","text_size":"normal_v2","element_id":"common_3_title"},{"tag":"markdown","content":"为进一步降低 AI 搜索接入门槛，平台现已支持提供**嵌入式、低代码的 UI 组件能力**，帮助企业以更低成本快速集成 **AI 对话助手、导购入口及交互页面**，减少前端开发与行为回流的接入复杂度。","text_align":"left","text_size":"normal_v2","element_id":"common_3_body"},{"tag":"img","img_key":"img_v2_9dd98485-2900-4d65-ada9-e31d1408dcfg","preview":true,"transparent":false,"scale_type":"fit_horizontal","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px","element_id":"common_3_picture"}],"padding":"12px 12px 12px 12px","direction":"vertical","horizontal_spacing":"8px","vertical_spacing":"8px","horizontal_align":"left","vertical_align":"top","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px","element_id":"section_common_3","weight":1}],"margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px"},{"tag":"hr","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px","element_id":"common_end"},{"tag":"markdown","content":"**Search**","text_align":"left","text_size":"heading","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px","icon":{"tag":"standard_icon","token":"history-search_outlined","color":"blue"},"element_id":"title_search"},{"tag":"column_set","horizontal_spacing":"8px","horizontal_align":"left","columns":[{"tag":"column","width":"weighted","background_style":"purple-50","elements":[{"tag":"markdown","content":"\n**<font color='purple'> 🎯 支持 “自带推荐物品列表” 能力</font>**","text_align":"left","text_size":"normal_v2","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px","element_id":"search_1_title"},{"tag":"markdown","content":"**支持传入自定义物品并灵活融合排序**：可在推荐 API 中直接传入候选物品列表，并与系统召回结果进行融合打分，既支持混合排序，也支持仅对客户自带物品进行排序返回，满足广告池、外部召回池及自定义候选集等多种场景需求。\n","text_align":"left","text_size":"normal_v2","margin":"0px 0px 8px 0px","element_id":"search_1_body"},{"tag":"img","img_key":"img_v2_9dd98485-2900-4d65-ada9-e31d1408dcfg","preview":true,"transparent":false,"scale_type":"fit_horizontal","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px","element_id":"search_1_picture"}],"padding":"12px 12px 12px 12px","direction":"vertical","horizontal_spacing":"8px","vertical_spacing":"8px","horizontal_align":"left","vertical_align":"top","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px","element_id":"section_search_1","weight":1}],"margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px"},{"tag":"column_set","horizontal_spacing":"8px","horizontal_align":"left","columns":[{"tag":"column","width":"weighted","background_style":"purple-50","elements":[{"tag":"markdown","content":"\n**<font color='purple'> 🎯 支持 “自带推荐物品列表” 能力</font>**","text_align":"left","text_size":"normal_v2","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px","element_id":"search_2_title"},{"tag":"markdown","content":"**支持传入自定义物品并灵活融合排序**：可在推荐 API 中直接传入候选物品列表，并与系统召回结果进行融合打分，既支持混合排序，也支持仅对客户自带物品进行排序返回，满足广告池、外部召回池及自定义候选集等多种场景需求。\n","text_align":"left","text_size":"normal_v2","margin":"0px 0px 8px 0px","element_id":"search_2_body"},{"tag":"img","img_key":"img_v2_9dd98485-2900-4d65-ada9-e31d1408dcfg","preview":true,"transparent":false,"scale_type":"fit_horizontal","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px","element_id":"search_2_picture"}],"padding":"12px 12px 12px 12px","direction":"vertical","horizontal_spacing":"8px","vertical_spacing":"8px","horizontal_align":"left","vertical_align":"top","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px","element_id":"section_search_2","weight":1}],"margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px"},{"tag":"column_set","horizontal_spacing":"8px","horizontal_align":"left","columns":[{"tag":"column","width":"weighted","background_style":"purple-50","elements":[{"tag":"markdown","content":"\n**<font color='purple'> 🎯 支持 “自带推荐物品列表” 能力</font>**","text_align":"left","text_size":"normal_v2","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px","element_id":"search_3_title"},{"tag":"markdown","content":"**支持传入自定义物品并灵活融合排序**：可在推荐 API 中直接传入候选物品列表，并与系统召回结果进行融合打分，既支持混合排序，也支持仅对客户自带物品进行排序返回，满足广告池、外部召回池及自定义候选集等多种场景需求。\n","text_align":"left","text_size":"normal_v2","margin":"0px 0px 8px 0px","element_id":"search_3_body"},{"tag":"img","img_key":"img_v2_9dd98485-2900-4d65-ada9-e31d1408dcfg","preview":true,"transparent":false,"scale_type":"fit_horizontal","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px","element_id":"search_3_picture"}],"padding":"12px 12px 12px 12px","direction":"vertical","horizontal_spacing":"8px","vertical_spacing":"8px","horizontal_align":"left","vertical_align":"top","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px","element_id":"section_search_3","weight":1}],"margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px"},{"tag":"hr","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px","element_id":"search_end"},{"tag":"markdown","content":"**Recommendation**","text_align":"left","text_size":"heading","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px","icon":{"tag":"standard_icon","token":"thumbsup_outlined","color":"blue"},"element_id":"title_recommend"},{"tag":"column_set","flex_mode":"stretch","horizontal_spacing":"12px","horizontal_align":"left","columns":[{"tag":"column","width":"weighted","background_style":"wathet-50","elements":[{"tag":"markdown","content":"**<font color='wathet'>🏷️ 购物车推荐场景上线</font>**","text_align":"left","text_size":"normal_v2","element_id":"recommend_1_title"},{"tag":"markdown","content":"新增购物车推荐能力，支持传入多个父商品，平台基于多物品独立召回并智能融合，实时输出相关推荐结果，帮助电商客户提升客单价与整体收入。同时，控制台新增购物车场景类型及体验界面，并统一升级指定物品搜索框为置顶搜索，支持ID和名称模糊匹配。","text_align":"left","text_size":"normal_v2","margin":"0px 0px 8px 0px","element_id":"recommend_1_body"},{"tag":"img","img_key":"img_v2_9dd98485-2900-4d65-ada9-e31d1408dcfg","preview":true,"transparent":false,"scale_type":"fit_horizontal","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px","element_id":"recommend_1_picture"},{"tag":"div","text":{"tag":"plain_text","content":"","text_size":"normal_v2","text_align":"center","text_color":"default"},"margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px"}],"padding":"12px 12px 12px 12px","direction":"vertical","horizontal_spacing":"8px","vertical_spacing":"4px","horizontal_align":"left","vertical_align":"top","element_id":"section_recommend_1","weight":1}],"margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px"},{"tag":"column_set","horizontal_spacing":"8px","horizontal_align":"left","columns":[{"tag":"column","width":"weighted","background_style":"wathet-50","elements":[{"tag":"markdown","content":"**<font color='wathet'> 🏷️ 支持搜索分类统计能力</font>**","text_align":"left","text_size":"normal_v2","element_id":"recommend_2_title"},{"tag":"markdown","content":"**聚合统计结果分类**：可基于指定字段对搜索结果进行聚合统计，并以分类标签形式返回，帮助用户快速理解结果分布。\n**结果页导航与筛选**：分类标签可直接用于搜索结果页的类别导航与条件筛选，提升结果浏览效率与筛选便捷性。\n**多类型字段配置**：支持字符串、布尔、数组及数值区间等多种字段类型的分面配置，满足不同业务场景下的灵活配置需求。","text_align":"left","text_size":"normal_v2","margin":"0px 0px 8px 0px","element_id":"recommend_2_body"},{"tag":"img","img_key":"img_v2_9dd98485-2900-4d65-ada9-e31d1408dcfg","preview":true,"transparent":false,"scale_type":"fit_horizontal","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px","element_id":"recommend_2_picture"}],"padding":"12px 12px 12px 12px","direction":"vertical","horizontal_spacing":"8px","vertical_spacing":"8px","horizontal_align":"left","vertical_align":"top","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px","element_id":"section_recommend_2","weight":1}],"margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px"},{"tag":"column_set","horizontal_spacing":"8px","horizontal_align":"left","columns":[{"tag":"column","width":"weighted","background_style":"wathet-50","elements":[{"tag":"markdown","content":"**<font color='wathet'> 🏷️ 支持搜索分类统计能力</font>**","text_align":"left","text_size":"normal_v2","element_id":"recommend_3_title"},{"tag":"markdown","content":"**聚合统计结果分类**：可基于指定字段对搜索结果进行聚合统计，并以分类标签形式返回，帮助用户快速理解结果分布。\n**结果页导航与筛选**：分类标签可直接用于搜索结果页的类别导航与条件筛选，提升结果浏览效率与筛选便捷性。\n**多类型字段配置**：支持字符串、布尔、数组及数值区间等多种字段类型的分面配置，满足不同业务场景下的灵活配置需求。","text_align":"left","text_size":"normal_v2","margin":"0px 0px 8px 0px","element_id":"recommend_3_body"},{"tag":"img","img_key":"img_v2_9dd98485-2900-4d65-ada9-e31d1408dcfg","preview":true,"transparent":false,"scale_type":"fit_horizontal","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px","element_id":"recommend_3_picture"}],"padding":"12px 12px 12px 12px","direction":"vertical","horizontal_spacing":"8px","vertical_spacing":"8px","horizontal_align":"left","vertical_align":"top","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px","element_id":"section_recommend_3","weight":1}],"margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px"},{"tag":"hr","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px","element_id":"recommend_end"},{"tag":"markdown","content":"**Chat**","text_align":"left","text_size":"heading","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px","icon":{"tag":"standard_icon","token":"chat-news_outlined","color":"blue"},"element_id":"title_chat"},{"tag":"column_set","horizontal_spacing":"8px","horizontal_align":"left","columns":[{"tag":"column","width":"weighted","background_style":"green-50","elements":[{"tag":"markdown","content":"**<font color='green'> 🏷️ 支持搜索分类统计能力</font>**","text_align":"left","text_size":"normal_v2","element_id":"chat_1_title"},{"tag":"markdown","content":"**聚合统计结果分类**：可基于指定字段对搜索结果进行聚合统计，并以分类标签形式返回，帮助用户快速理解结果分布。\n**结果页导航与筛选**：分类标签可直接用于搜索结果页的类别导航与条件筛选，提升结果浏览效率与筛选便捷性。\n**多类型字段配置**：支持字符串、布尔、数组及数值区间等多种字段类型的分面配置，满足不同业务场景下的灵活配置需求。","text_align":"left","text_size":"normal_v2","margin":"0px 0px 8px 0px","element_id":"chat_1_body"},{"tag":"img","img_key":"img_v2_9dd98485-2900-4d65-ada9-e31d1408dcfg","preview":true,"transparent":false,"scale_type":"fit_horizontal","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px","element_id":"chat_1_picture"}],"padding":"12px 12px 12px 12px","direction":"vertical","horizontal_spacing":"8px","vertical_spacing":"8px","horizontal_align":"left","vertical_align":"top","margin":"0px 0px 0p